{"tid":2190726,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"與學生互傳色慾照　28歲女教師判囚近4年","createTime":"2020-09-06T02:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T03:36:35.000Z","uid":75256,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1282d447e815b3ab186756bdc1a1afbf1ac74bae","tid":2190726,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/pe-teacher-sentenced-over-after-secret-affair-with-14-year-old-student\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fpe-teacher-sentenced-over-after-secret-affair-with-14-year-old-student&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR6WONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=3e06f9d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/pe-teacher-sentenced-over-after-secret-affair-with-14-year-old-student</a><br />\n<br />\n新州一名28歲已婚女教師與學生發展不倫關係，法庭聆悉她在跟丈夫關係瀕臨破裂期間，只因想吸引男人注意而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n《每日電訊報》報道，案情透露，在2018年，涉案的新州Hunter區體育女教師Katie Smith，與時年14歲的男學生發展不倫關係，包括互傳色慾照片和影片，之後再有數次秘密約會。<br />\n<br />\n法庭聆悉，被告從沒想跟事主性交，只是想獲稱讚漂亮。根據一份呈堂報告，被告「需要被認同」和渴望得到男人的注意。<br />\n<br />\n昨日（9月4日）在新州Newcastle地區法院，被告被判監禁3年10個月，其中兩年3個月不准假釋。<br />\n<br />\n法官Kara Shead批評，被告失信於事主，事主有權感受到被告的保護而覺得安全，「她利用了學生的脆弱。這是嚴重的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n警方提交的案情摘要，列出了被告如何跟事主在交友程式Snapchat上做朋友，並「模糊了」師生的界線。<br />\n<br />\n在一星期內，兩人交換了色慾照片和影片，包括被告傳出自己胸部的照片、揉搓陰部的影片，事主則傳出自己陰莖勃起的照片。<br />\n<br />\n兩人最終多次秘密約會，包括兩次在學校儲物房，以及聖誕節假期在停車場。他們在這些地方接吻和互相撫摸。<br />\n<br />\n他們的行為在2018年第4學期至2019年第1學期之間發生。<br />\n<br />\n最終東窗事發，是被告發現自己的色情照片在學校流傳，以及事主向母親坦誠交代。事主母親報警後，被告遭到拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n她承認誘使兒童進行非法的性活動、非禮16歲以下人士、蓄意性觸碰10至16歲兒童。<br />\n<br />\n檢控官Kristy Mulley表示，案中出現「權力不平衡」和「精神勾結」。她批評，被告濫用自己為人師表的身份。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師John O&rsquo;Sullivan較早前請求法官不判監禁，並說獄中無法治療被告。<br />\n<br />\n他在庭上表示，被告受到父親家暴，曾就性侵犯問題致電求助，「似乎被告是個想引人注意的人。她對其行為負上全責，並且向受害人表達同情。她不只失去工作，還失去事業。她已經知錯了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nnimgt-a.akamaihd.net/transform/v1/crop/frm/v6ZqFubQfSczSV22Th78nc/ea7e922d-78c0-4920-a18c-dd788da04c77.JPG/r0_1986_3375_5380_w1200_h678_fmax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnnimgt-a.akamaihd.net%2Ftransform%2Fv1%2Fcrop%2Ffrm%2Fv6ZqFubQfSczSV22Th78nc%2Fea7e922d-78c0-4920-a18c-dd788da04c77.JPG%2Fr0_1986_3375_5380_w1200_h678_fmax.jpg&h=eb4f5d2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"781762b438219427a274c67c8de01c6c988e09d9","tid":2190726,"uid":75256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"我講過好多次！"},{"pid":"a44bf6546a4277cdd75e3e36ccdaec6204c8f41f","tid":2190726,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c457e10ca201f01e6c7a3b21c2e234710ed8119a","tid":2190726,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"14歲男學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嫩口"},{"pid":"4e940e74aa1beef92529ea80c2b28b278318cc9d","tid":2190726,"uid":32150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bc60618c4c1736abc95d06095a7ec2c3d8a7d3","tid":2190726,"uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"又係呢d傻9<br />\n食完唱"},{"pid":"e1a2658225eca137c2cfb9460faee820847de643","tid":2190726,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2692fa57b5bb0f3ad0e2b52020bccc1c202c50","tid":2190726,"uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1a2658225eca137c2cfb9460faee820847de643","tid":2190726,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":